\nabla \dfrac 1 {|\vec{r}|} \equiv -\dfrac {\vec{r}} {|\vec{r}|^3}
\nabla \dfrac 1 {|\vec{r}-\vec{a}|} = -\dfrac {\vec{r}-\vec{a}} {|\vec{r}-\vec{a}|^3}
\vec{a}
\vec{r} = r\hat{r}
\nabla f(r) \equiv \dfrac{\vec{r}}{r}\space f'(r)
\nabla_j \frac 1 {|\vec{r}-\vec{a}|}=\frac{\partial}{\partial x^j}\left(\sum_{i=1}^n(x^i-a^i)^2\right)^{-\frac{1}{2}}.
